{"tid":620723,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"爭取連仔開個APPLE台!!!!!!","createTime":"2018-04-07T18:05:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T02:08:19.000Z","uid":78533,"like":44,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a4949a4eee63894146cdf97cea870ad8e869cbe0","tid":620723,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T18:05:17.000Z","msg":"其實真係好需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n班盲粉乜 AN POST都衝入黎 鳩叫~<br />\n<br />\n3星 狗也不屌<br />\n小米華為大陸機 狗也不屌<br />\nSONY 系統差ZX2樣柒 狗也不屌<br />\nLG用1年就 LAG爆 狗也不屌<br />\nHTC 乜仲未收皮咩 狗也不屌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 實情係因為佢地咁諗野<br />\n<br />\n以下係APPLE狗既邏輯<br />\n<br />\n見到APPLE 龍汁四射<br />\nAPPLE變慢 用家問題<br />\nAPPLEM字額 睇下就慣<br />\nAPPLE唔用指紋 FACEID先係人類最好解鎖方法(禁一下再用FACE解鎖)(指紋:禁一下同時解鎖)<br />\nAPPLE爆炸 用家問題<br />\nAPPLEOLED壞MON用家問題<br />\n<br />\n所有用得唔好 系統唔方便都只會係其他用家問題 <br />\n最重要係個系統十年如一日 ICLOUD用兩用就爆位 要課金<br />\n<br />\n但係~都唔係最主要問題,因為如果有乜問題都係個別用家問題<br />\n結論買黎打飛機好抵!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最好笑明明IP8同IPX都係2017機但就笑鳩IP8係考古<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> 如果連仔仲唔分台既~手機台一日都唔會有正常討論<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"020ca744462e21597ea701bba7680f465e15e5da","tid":620723,"uid":43178,"like":30,"dislike":9,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T18:08:02.000Z","msg":"應該係an狗去黑洞開po<br />\n諗下點解有有連登先啦"},{"pid":"8a29e89f8b846414f137b50a2206cd8843c3b619","tid":620723,"uid":43178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T18:08:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該係an狗去黑洞開po<br />\n諗下點解有連登先啦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"decf0ed573786cf11e56d32ceb08d51c1bc999d1","tid":620723,"uid":21423,"like":9,"dislike":9,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T18:14:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"35bd1a72eac95b17d2d2bafc4a0e448207d0ccbf","tid":620723,"uid":35070,"like":0,"disli